{"id":31077,"title":"[Does the use of psychoactive drugs in adolescence create specific problems?].","abstract":"The use of psychoactive drugs by teenagers presents commonalities and specificities depending on the substances used. The connection noted between the early age of use and the onset of harm, supports the recommendation of early interventions targeting all drugs. However, drug use differs according to the type of substance, highlighting the need to take into accountthese specificities in addiction therapy.","date":"2014-01-13","categories":"Chemically-Induced Disorders","split":"test","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24409574","annotations":[{"name":"Recreational drug use","weight":0.801843,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Recreational_drug_use"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.801843,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Adolescence","weight":0.801318,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adolescence"},{"name":"Psychoactive drug","weight":0.749237,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Psychoactive_drug"},{"name":"Drug","weight":0.749237,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Drug"},{"name":"Substance dependence","weight":0.672147,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Substance_dependence"},{"name":"Enzyme","weight":0.426731,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Enzyme"},{"name":"Chemical substance","weight":0.408786,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chemical_substance"},{"name":"Absorption (pharmacokinetics)","weight":0.136585,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Absorption_(pharmacokinetics)"},{"name":"Intervention (counseling)","weight":0.122093,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Intervention_(counseling)"}]}
